prompts.frontCover:
A full-shot, 2D flat illustration for a birthday card front cover, in the style of a lighthearted watercolor painting. The scene is a sunny beach with gentle ocean waves in the background. In the center, an elderly Asian woman, "Lao Lao," sits majestically on a large throne constructed entirely from mahjong tiles. She is depicted as a cartoon queen, wearing a small, playful crown and a big, happy smile, holding a giant bubble tea with both hands. To her left, stands a cartoon version of a young man with short, slightly tousled black hair, wearing a white short-sleeved t-shirt, captured with a broad, warm, cheerful smile showing very white teeth. To her right, stands a cartoon version of a young woman with long, straight black hair past her shoulders, wearing thin, gold-rimmed circular glasses and a yellow sundress with a red floral pattern, smiling happily and contentedly. The style is soft and flowing, with visible artistic brush strokes, organic paint bleeds, and a subtle paper texture. In the center of the scene, in a clear area, the words "Happy Birthday" are written in a beautiful, readable, handwritten cursive script. --ar 5:7 --style raw --v 6.0

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
